n active while `isSubmitting`. Drawer also closes unconditionally. Can hide in-flight errors.\r\n1324: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Disable close button and block drawer close while `isSubmitting`.\r\n1325: - **├É┬á├É┬╡├É┬│├æΓé¼├É┬╡├æ┬ü├æ┬ü├É┬╕├æ┬Å:** BUG-PM-034 (S85)\r\n1326: \r\n1327: ### BUG-PM-032: Order-status differentiation regressed (P2)\r\n1328: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P2\r\n1329: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S116 (Codex review)\r\n1330: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** CartView.jsx:240\r\n1331: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** `getSafeStatus()` missing `accepted` fallback. Render paths ignore `status.icon`. Sent/accepted/cooking/ready collapse into near-identical text.\r\n1332: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Add `accepted` to fallback map. Render `{icon} {label}` in all badge locations.\r\n1333: - **├É┬á├É┬╡├É┬│├æΓé¼├É┬╡├æ┬ü├æ┬ü├É┬╕├æ┬Å:** BUG-PM-019\r\n1334: \r\n1335: ### BUG-PM-033: Scroll position not reset after table verification (P2)\r\n1336: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P2\r\n1337: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S116 (Codex review)\r\n1338: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** CartView.jsx:136\r\n1339: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** `isTableVerified` effect only resets attempt counters, scroll-to-top fix is gone. Drawer stays stranded at bottom after code entry.\r\n1340: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Restore scroll reset using `prevTableVerifiedRef` and nearest scrollable ancestor.\r\n1341: - **├É┬á├É┬╡├É┬│├æΓé¼├É┬╡├æ┬ü├æ┬ü├É┬╕├æ┬Å:** BUG-PM-S81-03\r\n1342: \r\n1343: ### BUG-PM-034-R: Guest code leaked back into drawer header (P2)\r\n1344: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P2\r\n1345: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S116 (Codex review)\r\n1346: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** CartView.jsx:274,281\r\n1347: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** `#guestCode` appended to \"├ÉΓÇÖ├æΓÇ╣:\" label, exposing internal identifier even when `hallGuestCodeEnabled` is off.\r\n1348: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Show code only in dedicated waiter-code block.\r\n1349: - **├É┬á├É┬╡├É┬│├æΓé¼├É┬╡├æ┬ü├æ┬ü├É┬╕├æ┬Å:** BUG-PM-020\r\n1350: \r\n1351: ### BUG-PM-035: Verified-table block regresses mobile UX (P2)\r\n1352: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P2\r\n1353: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S116 (Codex review)\r\n1354: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** CartView.jsx:1046,1007,1056\r\n1355: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** Duplicate \"├É┬í├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╗ ├É┬┐├É┬╛├É┬┤├æΓÇÜ├É┬▓├É┬╡├æΓé¼├É┬╢├É┬┤├É┬╡├É┬╜\" header after verification. Info buttons are tiny icon-only touch targets (< 44px).\r\n1356: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Restore `shouldShowOnlineOrderBlock` logic. Replace icon-only info controls with 44px labeled buttons.\r\n1357: - **├É┬á├É┬╡├É┬│├æΓé¼├É┬╡├æ┬ü├æ┬ü├É┬╕├æ┬Å:** BUG-PM-008, BUG-PM-S81-07\r\n1358: \r\n1359: ### BUG-PM-036: Loyalty amounts bypass app localization (P2)\r\n1360: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P2\r\n1361: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S116 (Codex review)\r\n1362: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** CartView.jsx:398,922,925\r\n1363: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** Hard-coded `toLocaleString('ru-RU')` and `├óΓÇÜ┬╕` instead of `formatPrice`. Wrong currency/locale for non-Russian/non-tenge partners.\r\n1364: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Use same formatter/locale as rest of page.\r\n1365: \r\n1366: ### BUG-PM-037: Reward email flow reports success without validation (P2)\r\n1367: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P2\r\n1368: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S116 (Codex review)\r\n1369: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** CartView.jsx:514,520\r\n1370: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** Accepts any non-empty string, toasts \"Email saved!\" immediately. Invalid email or failed loyalty lookup still shows success.\r\n1371: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Validate email format, await persistence result, show error if failed.\r\n1372: \r\n1373: ### BUG-PM-038: Submit-error copy says \"order saved\" when it may not be (P2)\r\n1374: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P2\r\n1375: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S116 (Codex review)\r\n1376: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** CartView.jsx:1216, x.jsx:2591,2919\r\n1377: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** Error subtitle always says \"├ÉΓÇÖ├É┬░├æ╦å ├É┬╖├É┬░├É┬║├É┬░├É┬╖ ├æ┬ü├É┬╛├æΓÇª├æΓé¼├É┬░├É┬╜├É┬╡├É┬╜. ├É┼╕├É┬╛├É┬┐├æΓé¼├É┬╛├É┬▒├æ╞Æ├É┬╣├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡ ├æ┬ü├É┬╜├É┬╛├É┬▓├É┬░\" but submit may have failed completely. Misleads guest.\r\n1378: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Use neutral retry text, or pass explicit error type.\r\n1379: \r\n1380: ### BUG-PM-039: 8-digit table codes overflow narrow phones (P2)\r\n1381: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P2\r\n1382: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S116 (Codex review)\r\n1383: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** CartView.jsx:100,1074\r\n1384: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** Config allows up to 8 slots, but fixed `w-9` boxes + `gap-2` exceeds 320px viewport.\r\n1385: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Make slot width/gap responsive, or switch to single-input layout for longer codes.\r\n1386: \r\n1387: ### BUG-PM-040: Loyalty points debited before order creation ├óΓé¼ΓÇ¥ no rollback on failure (P0)\r\n1388: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P0\r\n1389: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S119 (CC review)\r\n1390: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** x.jsx:2443-2455, x.jsx:2817-2829\r\n1391: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** In both `processHallOrder` and pickup/delivery flow, `LoyaltyTransaction` (redeem) and `LoyaltyAccount.update` (balance decrement) execute BEFORE `Order.create`. If order creation throws, points are permanently lost ├óΓé¼ΓÇ¥ catch block only sets `submitError`, never re-credits.\r\n1392: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Move points deduction to after `Order.create` succeeds, or add compensating re-credit in catch block.\r\n1393: \r\n1394: ### BUG-PM-041: Polling timer leak in useTableSession after cleanup (P0)\r\n1395: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P0\r\n1396: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S119 (CC review)\r\n1397: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** useTableSession.jsx:670-685\r\n1398: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** `scheduleNext()` creates recursive `setTimeout` chain. Cleanup sets `cancelled=true` and `clearTimeout(intervalId)`, but if `pollSessionData()` is mid-execution during cleanup, `scheduleNext` inside the callback fires, registering a new timeout the cleanup can't clear. Orphaned polling causes spurious state updates on stale components.\r\n1399: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Guard `scheduleNext` with `if (cancelled) return` before scheduling next poll.\r\n1400: \r\n1401: ### BUG-PM-042: isBillOnCooldown crashes in restricted environments (P1)\r\n1402: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P1\r\n1403: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S119 (CC review)\r\n1404: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** x.jsx:283-288\r\n1405: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** `isBillOnCooldown()` calls `localStorage.getItem()` without try/catch. In private/incognito mode or strict security policies, `localStorage` access can throw. Called inside `useEffect` at x.jsx:2256 ├óΓé¼ΓÇ¥ unhandled exception crashes the component.\r\n1406: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Add try/catch with `return false` fallback inside `isBillOnCooldown`.\r\n1407: \r\n1408: ### BUG-PM-043: formatOrderTime and OrderStatusScreen.formatPrice hardcode ru-RU locale (P2)\r\n1409: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P2\r\n1410: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S119 (CC review)\r\n1411: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** x.jsx:973, x.jsx:1206\r\n1412: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** `formatOrderTime` uses `d.toLocaleTimeString(\"ru-RU\", ...)` and `OrderStatusScreen.formatPrice` uses `num.toLocaleString(\"ru-RU\")`, ignoring active `lang` state. Wrong locale for non-Russian partners.\r\n1413: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Pass `lang` or the parent's `formatPrice` as prop to `OrderStatusScreen`. Make `formatOrderTime` locale-aware.\r\n1414: - **├É┬í├É┬▓├æ┬Å├É┬╖├É┬░├É┬╜├É┬╛:** BUG-PM-036 (same pattern in CartView)\r\n1415: \r\n1416: ### BUG-PM-044: loyalty_redeem_rate falsy-coalescing shows wrong monetary value (P2)\r\n1417: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P2\r\n1418: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S119 (CC review)\r\n1419: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** CartView.jsx:925\r\n1420: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** `(partner?.loyalty_redeem_rate || 1)` treats rate of `0` as falsy, falls back to `1`. Partner with explicit `loyalty_redeem_rate = 0` shows inflated value to guests.\r\n1421: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Use `??` (nullish coalescing) instead of `||`: `(partner?.loyalty_redeem_rate ?? 1)`.\r\n1422: \r\n1423: ### BUG-PM-045: console.log left in production order submission paths (P2)\r\n1424: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P2\r\n1425: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S119 (CC review)\r\n1426: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** x.jsx:2589, x.jsx:2917\r\n1427: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** Two `console.log(\"Order created\", order?.id)` calls remain in successful order submission paths (hall and pickup/delivery). Minor information leak, violates no-debug-log rule.\r\n1428: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Remove both `console.log` calls.\r\n1429: \r\n1430: ### BUG-PM-046: Redirect banner setTimeout not cleaned up on unmount (P2)\r\n1431: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P2\r\n1432: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S119 (CC review)\r\n1433: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** x.jsx:1871\r\n1434: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** `setTimeout(() => setRedirectBanner(null), 5000)` inside `useEffect` with no cleanup. If component unmounts or deps change within 5s, the stale timer fires `setRedirectBanner(null)` on an unmounted component ├óΓé¼ΓÇ¥ React dev warning.\r\n1435: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Store timer ID and return cleanup function, same pattern as `viewTransitionTimerRef`.\r\n1436: \r\n1437: ### BUG-PM-047: Multiple interactive elements missing aria-label (P3)\r\n1438: - **├É┼╕├æΓé¼├É┬╕├É┬╛├æΓé¼├É┬╕├æΓÇÜ├É┬╡├æΓÇÜ:** P3\r\n1439: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S119 (CC review)\r\n1440: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** CartView.jsx:424,449-450,1011,1060; MenuView.jsx:104,111,117\r\n1441: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** Icon-only buttons (call-waiter bell, name editor ├ó┼ôΓÇ£/├ó┼ôΓÇó, info ├óΓÇ£╦£ buttons, list-mode add/stepper buttons) use `title` instead of `aria-label` or have no accessible label at all. Screen readers and mobile VoiceOver can't announce button purpose.\r\n1442: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Add `aria-label` to all icon-only interactive elements. List-mode buttons should match tile-mode which already has proper labels.\r\n1443: \r\n1444: ---\r\n1445: \r\n1446: ## Fixed Bugs (├É┬╕├æ┬ü├É┬┐├æΓé¼├É┬░├É┬▓├É┬╗├É┬╡├É┬╜├æΓÇ╣)\r\n1447: \r\n1448: ### BUG-PM-023: reviewedItems.has() without null guard (P0) ├óΓé¼ΓÇ¥ FIXED S116\r\n1449: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S79 review (pre-existing from S74), fixed S116\r\n1450: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** CartView.jsx, Mode 2 order render\r\n1451: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** If `reviewedItems` prop is undefined, calling `.has()` crashes the render\r\n1452: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Added `safeReviewedItems = reviewedItems || new Set()` in safe prop defaults block. All `.has()` calls use safeReviewedItems.\r\n1453: \r\n1454: ### BUG-PM-024: loyaltyAccount.balance without null guard (P0) ├óΓé¼ΓÇ¥ FIXED S116\r\n1455: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S79 review (pre-existing from S74), fixed S116\r\n1456: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** CartView.jsx, loyalty section\r\n1457: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** If `loyaltyAccount.balance` is undefined/null, `.toLocaleString()` crashes\r\n1458: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Wrapped all `loyaltyAccount.balance` usages with `Number(loyaltyAccount.balance || 0)`.\r\n1459: \r\n1460: ### BUG-PM-025: draftRatings prop without null guard (P1) ├óΓé¼ΓÇ¥ FIXED S116\r\n1461: - **├É┼í├É┬╛├É┬│├É┬┤├É┬░:** S79 review (pre-existing from S74), fixed S116\r\n1462: - **├É┬ñ├É┬░├É┬╣├É┬╗:** CartView.jsx, Mode 2 order render\r\n1463: - **├É┬í├É┬╕├É┬╝├É┬┐├æΓÇÜ├É┬╛├É┬╝:** If `draftRatings` is undefined, accessing `draftRatings[itemId]` crashes\r\n1464: - **├É┬ñ├É┬╕├É┬║├æ┬ü:** Added `safeDraftRatings = draftRatings || {}` in safe prop defaults block. All `draftRatings[itemId]` uses safeDraftRatings.\r\n1465: \r\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
